This paper deals with image analysis and segmentation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of nature inspired algorithms such as Particle Swarm Optimization, Artificial Bee Colony Optimization and Differential Evolution suggests that this paper could also belong to the sub-categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper also deals with optimization and parameter tuning, which could place it in the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category.
